						               													<description>Totally Medieval is a game where you control opposing Armies. As you move closer to your opponent you will find new terrain and different weather systems which may help or hinder your progress. When you meet your opponent's army, be ready to attack and/or defend yourself so you can stop or slow down their advances on your homeland. Your survival is based on your success in keeping your opponent from advancing. Your goal is take over their homeland before they take yours.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the base game you will start as Viking or knights with other types of people to come later. Each type of person comes with historical aspect to each person on the team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game also comes with a great twist of the dice roll. In a game that would normally have a pair dice to roll and move your army's around you draw cards instead. These cards are call Math dice and they come in different levels of Math. Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, division and Algebra and all the choices you could use. Each player would draw a card and have the opponent draw it solve it to get a bonus for each battle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;So for this game you will learn a little fun history and solve a few math problems. With the upgraded armies to miniatures you gain a great chess set.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
